Package: pvm
Type: Package
Title: Package Version Manager for R
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Wush Wu
Maintainer: Wush Wu <wush@gmail.com>
Description: Export the installed packages and their version to a YAML file. 
  Users could import the list and install the binary package with the same version 
  from CRAN or MRAN(the historical snapshots of CRAN). If there is no specific binary
  package, the user could build it from source.
License: GPL(>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.0
Depends: R(>= 2.10)
Suggests: remotes, git2r, yaml
